<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>로그인 실패</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px;
        }
        .error-container {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .error-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .error-msg {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-title">❌ 비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.</div>
        <div class="error-msg">아이디와 비밀번호를 다시 확인해 주세요.</div>

        <a href="/user/login">🔑 다시 로그인하기</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>